 xattr Functions
 xattr




  &reftitle.intro;


    xattr extension allows to manipulate extended attributes on filesystems that support them.





   &reftitle.required;


    To use xattr, you will need libattr installed, available
    on the Linux XFS homepage &url.xattr;.



